What benefit has Tarceva shown during the studies?
For lung cancer, the median survival for the Tarceva patients was 6.7 months, compared with 4.7 months for the patients treated with placebo.
After 12 months, 31.2% of the patients taking erlotinib were still alive, compared with 21.5% of patients treated with placebo.
